### Navigation Management

Create database-driven navigation CRUD.

Fields:

* Module (enabled modules only)
* Parent navigation (optional)
* Name
* Code
* Icon
* Order (optional)

Rules:

* Auto assign order when empty: `max(order) + 1`
* Sort navigation by order
* Sort child items within parent
* Support hierarchical tree structure
* Include search, sorting, pagination, and icon picker

After navigation changes:

* Show refresh notification dialog
* Options:

  * Refresh Now
  * Later

